ozma-proxmox (1.0.0-1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * QEMU D-Bus display integration (Scanout framebuffer)
  * KVMFR/Looking Glass shared memory capture
  * D-Bus keyboard + mouse input injection
  * VM lifecycle hooks (start/stop/migrate)
  * VM profiles: gaming, workstation, server, media
  * Auto CPU pinning, hugepages, ReBAR detection
  * Multi-channel PipeWire audio
  * Per-VM display service (systemd template)
  * REST API extension (/api2/json/ozma/)
  * Auto-registration with ozma controller

